This paper deals with the optimization of power systems, which involves control and decision-making. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), which deals with the modeling, analysis, and control of complex systems. The paper also involves the use of algorithms and optimization techniques, which could place it in the cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) categories. The paper also deals with the integration of renewable energy sources, which could place it in the cs.ET (Energy and Power Systems) category. Finally, the paper deals with the operation of High Voltage Direct Current lines, which could place it in the cs.NE (Networks and Communications) category.
